Procurement.

!. Directory structure
.
`- pdz
    | - README - This file
    | - board - platform dependent files
    | - doc - documentation
    | - net_pack - description of network packets
    | - src - description of the technology of the device
    `- subsys - subsystems 
        | - boil - files related to the boiler
        | - cond - * to air conditioners
        | - devs - files of technological devices
        | - pdz - files related to PDV
        `- vent - * to ventilation systems
